relation: A Flower for Each of Them
She is made of what he remembers, of sunflowers and caring smiles.
And the breeze blows swiftly at their backs...
One for Hinawa, one for Flint, one for Claus. One for Duster, one for Kumatora, one for Boney. For each family, a bouquet.
All flowers bloom, and all flowers' petals eventually fall...
